{"tid":2272283,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"胸骨痛","createTime":"2020-11-05T03:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T07:44:10.000Z","uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"195d476d47e68b99cfa81bb0b847a3e81f61d9e2","tid":2272283,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:35:46.000Z","msg":"之前意外撞到個心口位，當時係抖唔到氣一小段時間，然後冇乜事。去左中醫到睇條頸，敷左幾日藥咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到前排去左正骨，比佢整完之後個胸位頂住勁唔舒服，由個胸骨扯住上條頸到，宜家每日要擴胸同埋搵野頂一頂個心口，心口中間個骨啪一聲先至叫舒服d。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇人有類似情況? 諗緊係去睇脊醫定中醫比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9f4e753b7c7e8e4ca513e0354227ab3e1fdee8","tid":2272283,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"物理治療師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8551bb545e4e74b762087abd75fc183470808af9","tid":2272283,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9f4e753b7c7e8e4ca513e0354227ab3e1fdee8","tid":2272283,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"物理治療師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:50:45.000Z","msg":"try 過?"},{"pid":"37a9a073983cb090ff3e61a38b3f61a73e554c19","tid":2272283,"uid":192551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:26:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7c86fe2ce3aa98405f20fd8b39de01c6d41056bd","tid":2272283,"uid":373626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba9f4e753b7c7e8e4ca513e0354227ab3e1fdee8","tid":2272283,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"物理治療師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:43:42.000Z","msg":"之前手腕痛去睇 診金800 然後又話你依度痛嗰度有問題<br />\n照依樣依嗰樣收多咗我2650"}